  "text": "Results provided from the current study appear to support [CITATION_1] claim that mathematical understanding for teaching can be increased by a single course experience. However, I would argue that the post-test level of conceptual understanding demonstrated by many participants according to the current instrument is still highly inadequate for classroom teaching, and that more time must be allowed for such learning by preservice teachers if they are to teach effectively.",
